ArtyTorrent Pack 48-Downtempo Disco House Loops 110-119 bpm-WAV
---------------------------------------------------------------

The tempo is creeping up as we head towards the standard old skool house music bpm.
This pack has a disco vibe, with a mixture of solid 4/4 beats and syncopated percussion. 

Tempo ranges from 110-119 bpm.

Torrent contains 5 RAR files with 80 loops.
-------------------------------------------
4 on the floor 110-119 (10 loops)
Loopmasters Disco 110 (17 loops)
Loopmasters Disco House 115 (34 loops)
Misc Disco 110-119 (6 loops)
Misc Downtempo House 110-119 (13 loops)

All samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by Loopmasters, Sonic Foundry/Sony, and Ueberschall.
